signatures.text: inline fun <K, M : MutableMap<in K, in Char>> CharSequence.associateByTo( destination: M, keySelector: (Char) -> K): M
signatures.desc: Populates and returns the destination mutable map with key-value pairs, where key is provided by the keySelector function applied to each character of the given char sequence and value is the character itself.

signatures.text: inline fun <K, V, M : MutableMap<in K, in V>> CharSequence.associateByTo( destination: M, keySelector: (Char) -> K, valueTransform: (Char) -> V): M
signatures.desc: Populates and returns the destination mutable map with key-value pairs, where key is provided by the keySelector function and and value is provided by the valueTransform function applied to characters of the given char sequence.
